#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:1
msgid "YAML API"
msgstr "YAML API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:3
msgid ""
"YAML parsing and serialization helpers are available under `ptool.yaml` and "
"`p.yaml`."
msgstr "YAML 解析与序列化辅助能力位于 `ptool.yaml` 和 `p.yaml` 下。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:6
msgid "ptool.yaml.parse"
msgstr "ptool.yaml.parse"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:8
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:8"
msgid "`v0.4.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.4.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:10
msgid "`ptool.yaml.parse(input)` parses a YAML string into a Lua value."
msgstr "`ptool.yaml.parse(input)` 将 YAML 字符串解析为 Lua 值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:12
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:12"
msgid "`input` (string, required): The YAML text."
msgstr "`input`（string，必填）：YAML 文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:13
msgid "Returns: The parsed Lua value. The root can be any supported YAML type."
msgstr "返回：解析后的 Lua 值。根节点可以是任意受支持的 YAML 类型。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:15
msgid "Type mapping:"
msgstr "类型映射："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:17
msgid "YAML mapping -> Lua table"
msgstr "YAML mapping -> Lua table"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:18
msgid "YAML sequence -> Lua sequence table (1-based)"
msgstr "YAML sequence -> Lua 序列表（从 1 开始）"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:19
msgid "YAML string -> Lua string"
msgstr "YAML string -> Lua string"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:20
msgid "YAML integer that fits in `i64` -> Lua integer"
msgstr "可放入 `i64` 的 YAML integer -> Lua integer"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:21
msgid "Other YAML number -> Lua number"
msgstr "其他 YAML number -> Lua number"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:22
msgid "YAML boolean -> Lua boolean"
msgstr "YAML boolean -> Lua boolean"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:23
msgid "YAML null -> Lua `nil`"
msgstr "YAML null -> Lua `nil`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:25
msgid "Error behavior:"
msgstr "错误行为："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:27
msgid "An error is raised if `input` is not a string."
msgstr "如果 `input` 不是字符串，会抛出错误。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:28
msgid ""
"A YAML syntax error raises an error whose message includes parser detail."
msgstr "如果 YAML 语法有误，会抛出错误，错误信息中包含解析器细节。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:29
msgid ""
"An error is raised if the YAML value cannot be represented as a Lua value in "
"`ptool`, such as a mapping with non-string keys or an explicit YAML tag."
msgstr ""
"如果 YAML 值无法表示为 `ptool` 支持的 Lua 值，也会抛出错误，例如 非字符串 "
"key 的 mapping，或带显式 YAML tag 的值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:32
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:32"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:48
msgid "ptool.yaml.get"
msgstr "ptool.yaml.get"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:50
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:50"
msgid "`v0.4.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.4.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:52
msgid ""
"`ptool.yaml.get(input, path)` reads the value at a specified path from YAML "
"text."
msgstr "`ptool.yaml.get(input, path)` 从 YAML 文本中读取指定路径上的值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:55
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:55"
msgid "`input` (string, required): The YAML text."
msgstr "`input`（string，必填）：YAML 文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:56
msgid ""
"`path` ((string|integer)[], required): A non-empty path array, such as `{"
"\"spec\", \"template\", \"metadata\", \"name\"}` or `{\"items\", 1, \"name\""
"}`."
msgstr ""
"`path`（(string|integer)[]，必填）：非空路径数组，例如 `{\"spec\", "
"\"template\", \"metadata\", \"name\"}` 或 `{\"items\", 1, \"name\"}`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:58
msgid ""
"Returns: The corresponding Lua value, or `nil` if the path does not exist."
msgstr "返回：对应的 Lua 值；如果路径不存在，则返回 `nil`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:60
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:60"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:62
msgid "String path segments select mapping keys."
msgstr "字符串路径段用于选择 mapping key。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:63
msgid ""
"Integer path segments select sequence elements using Lua's 1-based indexing."
msgstr "整数路径段用于选择 sequence 元素，使用 Lua 的 1-based 索引。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:65
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:65"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:78
msgid "ptool.yaml.stringify"
msgstr "ptool.yaml.stringify"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:80
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:80"
msgid "`v0.4.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.4.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:82
msgid "`ptool.yaml.stringify(value)` converts a Lua value to YAML text."
msgstr "`ptool.yaml.stringify(value)` 将 Lua 值编码为 YAML 文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:84
msgid "`value` (YAML-compatible Lua value, required): The value to encode."
msgstr "`value`（兼容 YAML 的 Lua 值，必填）：要编码的值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:85
msgid "Returns: The encoded YAML string."
msgstr "返回：编码后的 YAML 字符串。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:87
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:87"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:89
msgid ""
"Values must be YAML-compatible through the same Lua value mapping used by "
"`ptool.json.stringify`."
msgstr "值必须能通过与 `ptool.json.stringify` 相同的 Lua 值映射表示为 YAML。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:91
msgid "Lua sequence tables are encoded as YAML sequences."
msgstr "Lua 序列表会编码为 YAML sequence。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:92
msgid "Lua string-keyed tables are encoded as YAML mappings."
msgstr "仅包含字符串 key 的 Lua table 会编码为 YAML mapping。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:94
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:94"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:106
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:108
msgid "Only single-document YAML is supported."
msgstr "目前只支持单文档 YAML。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:109
msgid "YAML mappings must use string keys."
msgstr "YAML mapping 的 key 必须是字符串。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:110
msgid "Explicit YAML tags are not supported."
msgstr "不支持显式 YAML tag。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:111
msgid ""
"The `path` argument for `ptool.yaml.get` must be a non-empty array of "
"strings and/or positive integers."
msgstr "`ptool.yaml.get` 的 `path` 参数必须是由字符串和/或正整数构成的非空数组。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/yaml.md:113
msgid "Integer path segments are 1-based so they match Lua array indexing."
msgstr "整数路径段为 1-based，以与 Lua 数组索引保持一致。"
